text: Johannes Härteis (born 22 February 1996) is a German tennis player. Härteis achieved a career high ATP singles ranking of world No. 345 in July 2019. He made his ATP main draw debut at the 2019 Hamburg European Open in the doubles competition, partnering Daniel Altmaier. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:German male tennis players Category:Sportspeople from Nuremberg
